OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy in the evening as rain spreads
OL,7,Fnortheast, heavier for a time in the
OL,8,Fwest. This clears overnight, becoming
OL,9,Fdry for a time, before further rain
OL,10,Freaches the west later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain in
OL,13,Fthe west at first. This spreading east
OL,14,Fand becoming heavy for a time. Then
OL,15,Fclearing to bright spells and showers
OL,16,Fin evening. Occasionally windy.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,19,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,20,Ffrom Monday to Wednesday, these heavy
OL,21,Fand thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
